Package: WordBox
Type: Package
Title: A Simple Vocabulary Trainer
Version: 0.2.1.9029
Author: Stefan Lanz
Maintainer: Stefan Lanz <slanz1137@gmail.com>
Description: A simple vocabulary trainer in the form of a shiny app.
 The user can create his own word lists in the form of csv-files.
 The interface is in German.
